From: OctaneOS <octaneos@local>
Date: Sat, 05 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] sound: add platform include path so adapter files find snd_sunxi_log.h

adapter/snd_sunxi_adapter.c and adapter/snd_sunxi_pcm_adapter.c include
"snd_sunxi_log.h" which lives in bsp/drivers/sound/platform/.  The
platform Makefile adds the adapter/ directory to ccflags but not the
platform/ directory itself, so the build fails with:

  fatal error: snd_sunxi_log.h: No such file or directory

Add the platform directory to ccflags so the include resolves correctly.

---
 bsp/drivers/sound/platform/Makefile | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/bsp/drivers/sound/platform/Makefile b/bsp/drivers/sound/platform/Makefile
index aaaaaa1..bbbbbbb 100644
--- a/bsp/drivers/sound/platform/Makefile
+++ b/bsp/drivers/sound/platform/Makefile
@@ -5,6 +5,7 @@
 # Copyright(c) 2022-2027 Allwinnertech Co., Ltd.

 ccflags-y += -I $(srctree)/bsp/drivers/sound/pa/
+ccflags-y += -I $(srctree)/bsp/drivers/sound/platform/
 ccflags-y += -I $(srctree)/bsp/drivers/sound/adapter
 ADPT_DIR := ../adapter
